    "Stewart Butterfield is the cofounder and former CEO of team-based messaging software Slack.",
    "In 2021, cloud software giant Salesforce acquired Slack for $27.7 billion in cash and stock.",
    "Butterfield departed Salesforce in 2022, amid an exodus of executives at the company.",
    "Butterfield and wife Jen Rubio, the founder of luggage startup Away, sold their San Francisco home and moved to Aspen in 2020.",
    "Though he cofounded a tech company, Butterfield proudly majored in philosophy as an undergraduate at Canada's University of Victoria."
  ],
